Name: subependymal glioma
Definition: A carcinoma that derives_from myoepithelial cells.

Name: myxopapillary ependymoma
Definition: A malignant glioma that is derived from ependymal cells

Name: cellular ependymoma
Definition: A dsDNA-RT virus infectious disease that results_in infection in animals and humans

Name: tanycytic ependymoma
Definition: A spinal cord glioma that has_material_basis_in cells linking the spinal cord central canal.
Synonym: Ependymal neoplasm of the Spinal Cord

Name: papillary ependymoma
Definition: A spinal cord glioma that has_material_basis_in cells linking the spinal cord central canal.
Synonym: Ependymal neoplasm of the Spinal Cord

Name: clear cell ependymoma
Definition: A spinal cord glioma that has_material_basis_in cells linking the spinal cord central canal.
Synonym: Ependymal neoplasm of the Spinal Cord
